"The user starts with View 1 (Overview) comparing metric distributions across status groups. Selecting a status filters Views 2-4. In View 2 (Exploration), users analyze CLTV-revenue patterns and select value ranges. View 3 (Exploration) reveals geographical hotspots through map brushing. View 4 (Exploration) identifies high-churn service bundles via treemap clicks. All selections feed into View 5 (Detail) showing demographic breakdowns of filtered cohorts through faceted bar charts."